query.name: LastAlerts
query.sql: select measure.id from measure, rule where (rule.machine=measure.machine) AND (rule.type=measure.type) AND ((measure.value < rule.min) OR (measure.value > rule.max)) order by measure.whenmeasured DESC

query.name: measureForMachineDate
query.sql: select measure.id from measure where ($machinekey=measure.machine) AND ($timestamp=measure.whenmeasured)
